@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "CSV 匯入";
}

<div class="lf-hint mb-3">
    <svg class="lf-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/img/icons.svg#info-circle"></use></svg>
    <span>匯入順序：先「使用者」、再「主機」、最後「群組授權」。</span>
    <button type="button" class="lf-help" tabindex="0" data-bs-toggle="popover" data-bs-trigger="focus"
            data-bs-title="為什麼有順序"
            data-bs-content="主機的負責人必須是已存在的使用者帳號，群組授權的兩端也必須是已存在的群組，因此要先匯入使用者、再主機、最後群組授權。">
        <svg class="lf-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="/img/icons.svg#question-circle"></use></svg>
    </button>
</div>

<div class="row g-3" id="import-cards">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="lf-card h-100">
            <div class="lf-card__header">
                <h2 class="lf-card__title">1. 使用者</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="lf-card__body">
                <p class="small text-muted">自然鍵：<code>account</code>。已存在則更新，不存在則新增。</p>
                <details class="mb-3">
                    <summary class="small text-muted mb-2" style="cursor:pointer">欄位格式說明</summary>
                    <div class="lf-table-wrap">
                    <table class="table table-sm small mb-0">
                        <thead><tr><th>欄位</th><th>必填</th><th>說明</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td><code>account</code></td><td>是</td><td>AD 帳號</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>display_name</code></td><td></td><td>空白＝不變</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>email</code></td><td></td><td>空白＝不變</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>groups</code></td><td></td><td>分號分隔；<strong>有值＝整組取代</strong>、空白＝不變</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>active</code></td><td></td><td>1 或 0，空白＝1</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    </div>
                </details>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary mb-2" href="/api/imports/Users/template">下載範本</a>
                <input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm" accept=".csv" data-upload="Users" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="lf-card h-100">
            <div class="lf-card__header">
                <h2 class="lf-card__title">2. 主機</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="lf-card__body">
                <p class="small text-muted">自然鍵：<code>host_name</code>。</p>
                <details class="mb-3">
                    <summary class="small text-muted mb-2" style="cursor:pointer">欄位格式說明</summary>
                    <div class="lf-table-wrap">
                    <table class="table table-sm small mb-0">
                        <thead><tr><th>欄位</th><th>必填</th><th>說明</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td><code>host_name</code></td><td>是</td><td>需與批次回報的機器名稱一致</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>ip_address</code></td><td></td><td>顯示用線索</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>netiq_server</code></td><td></td><td>所屬 Sentinel</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>role_desc</code></td><td></td><td>伺服器角色描述</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>groups</code></td><td></td><td>分號分隔；有值＝整組取代</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>owners</code></td><td></td><td>分號分隔的<strong>既有</strong>帳號</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>active</code></td><td></td><td>1 或 0</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    </div>
                </details>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary mb-2" href="/api/imports/Hosts/template">下載範本</a>
                <input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm" accept=".csv" data-upload="Hosts" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="lf-card h-100 lf-card--warning">
            <div class="lf-card__header">
                <h2 class="lf-card__title">3. 群組授權</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="lf-card__body">
                <p class="small text-muted">
                    <strong>全量取代</strong>：檔案就是授權的完整清單，
                    沒列出的既有授權會被移除（預覽會逐筆列出將被移除的項目）。
                </p>
                <details class="mb-3">
                    <summary class="small text-muted mb-2" style="cursor:pointer">欄位格式說明</summary>
                    <div class="lf-table-wrap">
                    <table class="table table-sm small mb-0">
                        <thead><tr><th>欄位</th><th>必填</th><th>說明</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td><code>user_group</code></td><td>是</td><td>既有的使用者群組名稱</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>host_group</code></td><td>是</td><td>既有的主機群組名稱</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    </div>
                </details>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary mb-2" href="/api/imports/GroupAccess/template">下載範本</a>
                <input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm" accept=".csv" data-upload="GroupAccess" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="lf-card h-100">
            <div class="lf-card__header">
                <h2 class="lf-card__title">負責人</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="lf-card__body">
                <p class="small text-muted">
                    指派主機的負責人。一台主機多列＝多位負責人；<strong>檔案中出現的主機，負責人整組取代</strong>。
                </p>
                <details class="mb-3">
                    <summary class="small text-muted mb-2" style="cursor:pointer">欄位格式說明</summary>
                    <div class="lf-table-wrap">
                    <table class="table table-sm small mb-0">
                        <thead><tr><th>欄位</th><th>必填</th><th>說明</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td><code>host_name</code></td><td>擇一</td><td>主機名稱（與 ip_address 至少填一個）</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>ip_address</code></td><td>擇一</td><td>host_name 空白時以此比對主機</td></tr>
                            <tr><td><code>owner_account</code></td><td>是</td><td>負責人帳號，<strong>不存在會自動建立</strong></td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    </div>
                </details>
                <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary mb-2" href="/api/imports/Owners/template">下載範本</a>
                <input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm" accept=".csv" data-upload="Owners" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="lf-card mt-3 d-none" id="preview-card">
    <div class="lf-card__header">
        <h2 class="lf-card__title">預覽 <span class="text-muted small" id="preview-file"></span></h2>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" id="preview-cancel">取消</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" id="preview-apply">套用</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lf-card__body">
        <div id="preview-summary" class="mb-3"></div>
        <div id="preview-warnings"></div>
        <div id="preview-rows"></div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="lf-card mt-3">
    <div class="lf-card__header">
        <h2 class="lf-card__title">匯入紀錄</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="lf-card__body p-0" id="import-logs"></div>
</div>

<div class="lf-card mt-3 d-none" id="encoding-note">
    <div class="lf-card__body small text-muted">
        檔案請存成 <strong>UTF-8</strong>。以 Excel 編輯時請選「CSV UTF-8」格式另存，
        否則中文欄位會變成亂碼。
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <script type="module" src="~/js/pages/imports.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
}
